avc_encode_webm
===============

This tool encode old videos into webm and mp4, and update the mediatype.
Webm and mp4 are necessary for the HTML5 page.

Requirements
-------------
Python 2.7 with psycopg2

Configuration
-------------

Configure the config.ini file :
* filename : the name for the log file
* pthscr : the path of the avc encoding scripts
* pthcours : the path of the avc courses
* interval : the courseid interval concerned
* host : database host
* port : database port
* dbname : database name
* user : database user
* password : database password
* owner_user : system user for the courses folders
* owner_group : system group for the courses folders

Run
---
python encode.py